---
import "/src/styles/global.css";
---
<!--
  Onepage-Design für fungery
-->

<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>fungery</title>

    <!-- SEO Basic -->
<title>fungery — agency for fungal x human relations</title>
<meta name="description" content="The Fungery shares mushroom knowledge through sensory and hands-on learning, brings people together, and provides temporary infrastructure for that purpose." />
<meta name="keywords" content="fungi, design, art, food, workshops, fermentation, sustainability, knowledge sharing, mycelium" />

<!-- Open Graph / Social Sharing -->
<meta property="og:title" content="fungery — agency for fungal x human relations" />
<meta property="og:description" content="Exploring human-fungal relations through sensory and collaborative formats." />
<meta property="og:type" content="website" />
<meta property="og:url" content="https://fungery.com" />
<meta property="og:image" content="/images/social-preview.jpg" />
<meta property="og:site_name" content="fungery" />

<!-- Twitter Card -->
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
<meta name="twitter:title" content="fungery — agency for fungal x human relations" />
<meta name="twitter:description" content="Exploring human-fungal relations through sensory and collaborative formats." />
<meta name="twitter:image" content="/images/social-preview.jpg" />

<!-- Favicon -->
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/fungery_favicon_32.png" />
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="64x64" href="/fungery_favicon_64.png" />


    <!-- Globale Styles (Farben, Schrift, Basisformatierung) -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/src/styles/global.css">

    <!-- Favicon für verschiedene Größen -->
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/fungery_favicon_16.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/fungery_favicon_32.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="48x48" href="/fungery_favicon_48.png">
<link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="64x64" href="/fungery_favicon_64.png">


    <!-- Seitenindividuelle Styles (Layout, Positionierung, Abstände etc.) -->
    <style>
      :root {
        --beige1: rgb(255, 244, 216);
        --beige2: rgb(244, 234, 207);
        --lila1: rgb(106, 99, 169);
        --lila2: rgb(89, 62, 142);
      }

      /* Grundstruktur */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        background-color: var(--lila1);
        color: var(--beige1);
      }

      main {
        margin-left: 200px; /* Platz für Navigation */
      }

      section {
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* ------------------- Navigation ------------------- */
      nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        height: 100vh;
        width: 200px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background-color: transparent;
        z-index: 1000;
      }

      nav a {
        color: var(--beige1);
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 1rem 0;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        color: var(--beige2);
      }

      /* Logo oben rechts führt zum Start */
      .top-logo {
        position: fixed;
        top: 1rem;
        right: 1.5rem;
        width: 80px;
        height: auto;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: none;
        box-shadow: none; /* kein Schatten */
        z-index: 1100;
      }

      /* ------------------- Start ------------------- */
      #start {
        background-color: var(--lila1);
        color: var(--lila1);
      }

      #start img {
        max-width: 1000px;
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
        box-shadow: none; /* kein Schatten */
      }

      /* ------------------- About ------------------- */
      #about {
        background-color: var(--lila1);
      }

      #about .textblock,
      #about .textblock-small {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
      }

      #about .image {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 1rem auto;
      }

      .caption {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--beige2);
      }

      /* ------------------- Workshops & Food ------------------- */
      .grid-4 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
      }

      .grid-4 img {
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
      }

      .photo-footer {
        margin-top: -1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--beige2);
      }

      #workshops p,
      #food p {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
      }

      /* ------------------- Kontakt ------------------- */
      #contact {
        background-color: var(--lila1);
      }

      /* ------------------- Footer ------------------- */
      footer {
        background-color: transparent;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      footer a {
        color: var(--beige1);
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 0.5rem;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
      }

      footer a:hover {
        color: var(--beige2);
      }

    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <!-- Logo oben rechts führt zum Start -->
    <a href="#start"><img src="/images/logo2.png" alt="fungery logo klein" class="top-logo" /></a>

    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#workshops">Workshops</a>
      <a href="#food">Food</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>

    <main>
      <!-- Start -->
      <section id="start">
        <img src="/images/logo3.png" alt="fungery logo groß" />
      </section>

      <!-- About -->
      <section id="about">
        <div class="image">
          <img src="/images/about.jpg" alt="fungery about" />
          <div class="caption">Photo: Lucas Melzer</div>
        </div>

        <h2>agency for fungal x human relations</h2>

        <div class="textblock">
The Fungery platform shares mushroom knowledge through sensory and hands‑on learning, brings people together, and provides temporary infrastructure for that purpose. Using fungi’s collaborative traits as a model, it invites participation from current and future mushroom enthusiasts. In doing so it creates a network of diverse actors that, like fungal mycelium, connects different organisms.        </div>

        <div class="image">
          <img src="/images/about2.jpg" alt="fungery about2" />
          <div class="caption">Photo: Isabel Hemberger</div>
        </div>

        <div class="textblock-small">
The temporary infrastructure consists of twelve stools, four tables, and a work table on casters. Visually and conceptually, the elements create a space that can be flexible and location-independent.        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Workshops -->
      <section id="workshops">
        <h2>Workshops</h2>
        <div class="grid-4">
          <img src="/images/ws1.jpg" alt="workshop 1" />
          <img src="/images/ws2.jpg" alt="workshop 2" />
          <img src="/images/ws3.jpg" alt="workshop 3" />
          <img src="/images/ws4.jpg" alt="workshop 4" />
        </div>
        <div class="photo-footer">Photos: Isabel Hemberger</div>

        <p>How can knowledge about mushrooms be shared? The fungery provides a flexible environment that can be set up anywhere. Using various tools and teaching concepts, the fungery explores how mushrooms can enrich the diversity of our diet and contribute to a more sustainable food culture. Here is a workshop on making tempeh. 
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Food -->
      <section id="food">
        <h2>Food</h2>
        <div class="grid-4">
          <img src="/images/food1.jpg" alt="food 1" />
          <img src="/images/food2.jpg" alt="food 2" />
          <img src="/images/food3.jpg" alt="food 3" />
          <img src="/images/food4.jpg" alt="food 4" />
        </div>
        <div class="photo-footer">Photos: kimchipowder</div>

        <p>
          Tastings and samplings as a tool for sensory experiences and exchange. The mushroom dinner from left to right: Hot Radishes, Tempeh Burger, Vanilla Shiitake Ice Cream, Umami Martini. Together with the 
          <a href="https://www.fermentierbar.de/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">fermentier.bar</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Kontakt -->
      <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>For inquiries and collaborations:</p>
        <p id="mail-container"></p>

        <script>
          const user = "mail";
          const domain = "fungery.com";
          const container = document.getElementById("mail-container");
          container.innerHTML = `<a href="mailto:${user}@${domain}" class="mail-link">${user}@${domain}</a>`;
        </script>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <footer>
        <a href="/imprint">Imprint</a> |
        <a href="/legal">Legal</a>
      </footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
